public class FirewallTLImpl<Identifier,MessageType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements TransportLayer<Identifier,MessageType>, TransportLayerCallback<Identifier,MessageType>

Drops all incoming TCP connections. Drops all incoming UDP connections that we didn't initiate, or that are since UDP_OPEN_MILLIS
